This is the corportate offices for the "Macrosoft
Corporation". It should be pretty fucking cool.

The floors are arranged in the following order:
   1 - Ground level
   2 - Grunt work offices
   3 - Low ranking company officers
   4 - Legal Dept (we are the borg...  you will be assimilated)
   5 - Weapons Research
   6 - Biological Research (Mutants...)
   7 - Bill's Lair (cultists and shit)

The level of the boss of each level follows the formula :
    x = 8 * (floor level) - 8

The common monsters are approximately half of the above.

-Cy    1 Aug 99

